{"tid":911450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國男殺死女友跳黃河自盡   因河水太凍爬上岸被捕","createTime":"2018-11-22T02:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T07:00:11.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f60fa00a893dcebc9a2c7b1add08210887452a0d","tid":911450,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:36:28.000Z","msg":"內蒙古呼和浩特一名楊姓男子周日因情海翻波連捅數刀殺死女友，其後到黃河邊投河自殺，惟他下水後感到河水冰冷，難忍低溫爬上岸，被趕到警員制服，目前案件仍在調查。<br />\n<br />\n楊男去年通過微信認識受害人，隨即發展成情侶。楊男十分珍惜這段感情，受害人提出分手令他感到絕望，分手當日楊男帶刀到受害人家中將她殺死。警方查看現場閉路電視，發現楊男當天上午駕着受害人的汽車離開，曾駛經當地一條村莊，遂派出9個小組追捕，至下午4時許在黃河的土右旗段中發現楊男，當場將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%83%85%E6%B5%B7%E7%BF%BB%E6%B3%A2%E6%AE%BA%E6%AD%BB%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E8%B7%B3%E9%BB%83%E6%B2%B3%E8%87%AA%E7%9B%A1-%E5%9B%A0%E6%B2%B3%E6%B0%B4%E5%A4%AA%E5%87%8D%E4%B8%8A%E5%B2%B8%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-231600009.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E8%25B7%25B3%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%259B%25A1-%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%25B2%25B3%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%2587%258D%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-231600009.html&d=Z5iWXm4WO3jE20R3F9d1rm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2395916d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%83%85%E6%B5%B7%E7%BF%BB%E6%B3%A2%E6%AE%BA%E6%AD%BB%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E8%B7%B3%E9%BB%83%E6%B2%B3%E8%87%AA%E7%9B%A1-%E5%9B%A0%E6%B2%B3%E6%B0%B4%E5%A4%AA%E5%87%8D%E4%B8%8A%E5%B2%B8%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-231600009.html</a>"},{"pid":"23d52455ff698dfd13831bb0234f4a41be4e95a3","tid":911450,"uid":20066,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T02:37:50.000Z","msg":"點解會笑撚左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4af03b9346ea6757e2174df4fc7abc3f678305b",